Date: Fri, 12 Aug 2016 16:51:33 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 14/56] net: thunderx: Add RGMII interface type support

This patch comes from Cavium online SDK OCTEONTX-SDK-6.1.0-PR.

It adds RGX/RGMII interface type support to BGX driver. This type of
interface is supported by 81xx SOC.

CN81XX VNIC has 8 VFs and max possible LMAC interfaces are 9,
hence RGMII interface will not work if all DLMs are in BGX mode
and all 8 LMACs are enabled

